01:37:45.361 --> 01:37:47.946
<i>giving one last kid to her husband.</i>

01:37:48.322 --> 01:37:49.782
Bitch! You're dead.

01:37:49.823 --> 01:37:52.284
<i>Did he implore her</i>
<i>to run away with him?</i>

01:37:52.451 --> 01:37:55.788
<i>Or did they both know someone had to stay,</i>

01:37:55.829 --> 01:38:00.793
<i>be the monster, pay the price,</i>
<i>and protect their secret?</i>

01:38:02.836 --> 01:38:07.466
<i>Whether she was a good person or not,</i>
<i>I'm still not sure,</i>

01:38:07.508 --> 01:38:12.096
<i>but my second mother loved me,</i>
<i>and I loved my second mother.</i>

01:38:19.186 --> 01:38:22.564
<i>My third mother is</i>
<i>teaching me about the bigger world.</i>

01:38:23.482 --> 01:38:28.946
<i>She says knowledge is the key</i>
<i>to open all my doors, so I stay focused.</i>

01:38:29.488 --> 01:38:32.366
<i>I observe, and I work hard.</i>

01:38:32.699 --> 01:38:34.159
Vera, sweetheart.

01:38:34.243 --> 01:38:36.328
<i>I listen to what she says</i>

01:38:36.578 --> 01:38:37.996
<i>I want to please her.</i>

01:38:38.247 --> 01:38:42.501
<i>My third mother loves me,</i>
<i>and I love my third mother.</i>

01:38:42.543 --> 01:38:44.628
You're going to be late for art class.

01:38:44.670 --> 01:38:46.296
I'll be right there.

01:38:58.267 --> 01:39:00.519
<i>My world has changed.</i>

01:39:01.770 --> 01:39:03.605
<i>I try to follow its rules.</i>

01:39:04.898 --> 01:39:07.484
<i>It's a beautiful world, my new mother says.</i>

01:39:09.069 --> 01:39:12.865
<i>She tells me to hang on, that I'm doing well,</i>

01:39:14.408 --> 01:39:16.201
<i>that I'll get used to it with time.</i>

01:39:21.665 --> 01:39:23.041
Jeffrey.

01:39:23.500 --> 01:39:25.419
Jeffrey, come on.

01:39:27.880 --> 01:39:29.465
Come on, honey.

01:39:30.007 --> 01:39:31.216
We're going to be late.

01:39:33.218 --> 01:39:35.554
<i>I'm not like the others.</i>

01:39:36.555 --> 01:39:38.390
<i>I guess they've forgotten.</i>

01:39:40.434 --> 01:39:41.810
<i>I can't</i>

01:39:48.775 --> 01:39:51.236
<i>Every morning,</i>
<i>I wake up to the same thought of</i>

01:39:51.320 --> 01:39:53.655
<i>giving it all up and running back home,</i>

01:39:54.364 --> 01:39:57.409
<i>but I remind myself I wanted this life.</i>

01:39:58.076 --> 01:40:01.079
<i>I wanted it. I made it happen.</i>

01:40:03.624 --> 01:40:06.001
<i>I guess it's better this way, right?</i>

01:40:07.586 --> 01:40:08.754
<i>Right?</i>

01:40:10.714 --> 01:40:11.882
<i>Right?</i>
